{NORTH has 17 points and might open 1NT. But with the 5-card Major suit she prefers 
to open 1\S.

SOUTH has excellent \S support but with 11 points is not quite strong enough to insist 
on reaching game. Instead he makes an invitational jump to 3\S, which NORTH is strong 
enough to raise to game.}

