{SOUTH has a solid 1\H opening, 14 points and five trumps.

NORTH must respond with 8 points, but cannot bid either minor suit since he needs at least 
11 points to bid a new suit at the 2-level. So he bids 1NT (6-10 points).

SOUTH doesn't object to Notrump so she passes.}

